commit_message: Updated process publish and output dir
Updated the publish directories output modes
Added a trim sequences process in the modules.nf to run trimmomatic on the sequnces.
Updated file paths in the parameters
Added the main.nf file that holds the main workflow and the modules that contain the sub workflow processes.
Added a base recalibration rule that performs the base recalibrations on the sequence file
Updated the convert sam to bam rule
Added a mark duplicates rule to find and mark any duplicates in the sequences.
Added a convert_sam_to_bam rule to convert the sam files to bam files
Update run alignment rule to run an alignment with bwa-mem2

Added a run alignment rule to run an alignment with bwa-mem2
Added a snakefile as the root of the analysis rules
Added a data.py file to handle matters involving data
Added a tools file in the analysis dir to handle matters involving galaxy analysis tools from the toolshed

Added an analysis dir with the 3 files: galaxy_instance.py to create a galaxy instance, history.py to handle the creation of the histories and the quality_control.py to handle the quality control check.
created a main.py file that initializes a connection to the galaxy servers and creates an galaxy instance.
